---
title: Topics
layout: layouts/base.njk
description: Explore the full curriculum in suggested order or jump to any topic.
permalink: /topics/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
{% set totalTopics = collections.learningPath | length %}
{% set totalBlocks = learningPath.blocks | length %}
{% set firstTopic = learningPath.blocks[0].topics[0] %}

<div class="topics-page">
  <h1>Topics</h1>
  <p class="topics-description">Explore {{ totalTopics }} articles across {{ totalBlocks }} blocks. Follow the suggested order or jump straight to the topic you need.</p>
  <div class="hero-actions topics-actions">
    <a href="/topics/{{ firstTopic.slug }}/" class="btn btn-primary">Start Learning</a>
    <a href="/glossary/" class="btn btn-secondary">Browse Glossary</a>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="features">
  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>{{ totalTopics }} articles</h3>
      <p>Each topic is a focused, standalone deep dive that still fits the larger sequence.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>{{ totalBlocks }} learning blocks</h3>
      <p>Topics are grouped by theme so you can build intuition before moving to advanced tools.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Suggested order</h3>
      <p>Read top-to-bottom for a guided path, or jump into any block whenever you need.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="learning-path">
  <div class="learning-path-content">
    <h2 class="learning-path-title">Curriculum Map</h2>
    <p class="learning-path-description">Browse every block and topic in the recommended sequence.</p>
    <ol class="learning-path-blocks">
      {% for block in learningPath.blocks %}
      <li class="learning-path-block">
        <div class="learning-path-block-header">
          <span class="learning-path-block-number">{{ loop.index }}</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="learning-path-block-title">{{ block.title }}</h3>
            <p class="learning-path-block-meta">{{ block.topics | length }} topics</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="learning-path-topics">
          {% for topic in block.topics %}
          <li class="learning-path-topic">
            <a href="/topics/{{ topic.slug }}/">{{ topic.title }}</a>
          </li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>
